        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This staff is tapered at the base and carved into a gem-studded twist at the top. While wielding the staff, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to checks to identify evocation magic.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Ray of Frost]{Ray of Frost}</em></li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Magic Missile]{Magic Missile}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Shocking Grasp]{Shocking Grasp}</em></li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Acid Arrow]{Acid Arrow}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Glitterdust]{Glitterdust}</em></li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Lightning Bolt]{Lightning Bolt}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Magic Missile]{Magic Missile}</em></li>\n<li><strong>4th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Fireball]{Fireball}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Weapon Storm]{Weapon Storm}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>"
